	<h1 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-176853795" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/25/03/29/0435221/as-the-arctics-winter-sea-ice-hits-a-new-record-low---what-happens-next">As the Arctic's Winter Sea Ice Hits a New Record Low - What Happens Next?</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.msn.com/en-us/weather/climate-change/winter-sea-ice-in-the-arctic-just-hit-a-record-low/ar-AA1BRoHc"  title="External link - https://www.msn.com/en-us/weather/climate-change/winter-sea-ice-in-the-arctic-just-hit-a-record-low/ar-AA1BRoHc" target="_blank"> (msn.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-176853795" >64</span>-->
		

		
		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//news.slashdot.org/story/25/03/29/0435221/as-the-arctics-winter-sea-ice-hits-a-new-record-low---what-happens-next#comments" title="">64</a></span>
		
	</h1>
	<div class="details" id="details-176853795">
		<span class="story-details">
		<span class="story-views">
			<span class="sodify" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better"></span><span class="icon-beaker pop1 " alt="Popularity" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')"><span></span></span> 
		</span>
		</span>
		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  EditorDavid
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-176853795" datetime="on Saturday March 29, 2025 @11:34AM">on Saturday March 29, 2025 @11:34AM</time>
		
		
			 from the <span class="dept-text">hot-water</span> dept.
		
		</span>
